</ul><h2 id="f1-the-movie-december-12"><a href="https://apple.co/3KFYL9B" rel="noopener noreferrer">F1: The Movie</a> (December 12)</h2>
<p id="p22">The biggest event of December for Apple TV is the streaming debut of F1: The Movie. The film has been available to buy or rent for a while after playing in theaters last summer, and now it will be available to stream as part of an Apple TV subscription, too. I haven&rsquo;t seen F1 since WWDC in June, so I&rsquo;m looking forward to rewatching it with my family over the holidays.</p>
