<h2 id="a-charlie-brown-christmas-streaming-free-december-13-14"><a href="https://apple.co/48Ct74N" rel="noopener noreferrer">A Charlie Brown Christmas</a> (Streaming Free, December 13-14)</h2>
<p id="p27">Apple has run Charlie Brown holiday specials since 2020 and will continue to do so <a href="https://www.apple.com/tv-pr/news/2025/10/apple-tv-is-the-exclusive-streaming-home-until-2030/" rel="noopener noreferrer">until at least 2030</a>. As was the case last year, A Charlie Brown Christmas will be available to stream for free for two days: December 13 and 14. So whether you have <a href="https://apple.co/4qzBMwS" rel="noopener noreferrer">an Apple TV subscription</a> or not, you can get your traditional Peanuts holiday fix soon.</p>
