</ul><h2 id="born-to-be-wild-december-19"><strong><a href="https://apple.co/44Hc40f" rel="noopener noreferrer">Born to be Wild</a></strong> (December 19)</h2>
<p id="p31">Born to Be Wild is a new natural-history docu-series that follows the upbringing of six endangered baby animals by their human protectors.</p>
